					<div style="float:left;"><strong class="xar-sub">Subject:<a name="83965" href="http://www.ldonline.org/xarbb/topic/13689#83965">Re: Writing, reading comprehension &amp;amp; handwriting problems (l
</a></strong></div>
					<div style="clear: both;"></div>
				</div>
				<div style="clear: left;">
															<p>I would have him re-tested by a neuropsychologist across all domains to find out where his issues are. The gap between his verbal and performance show there is definitely some serious LDs going on. Getting things sorted out may help you find the proper therapies to help him succeed.</p>
																		<p class="hiddensignature">scifinut
mom to: ms 16, bp/adhd/anxiety/complex ld
mr. 20, add/dyslexic

I hear and I forget
I see and I remember
I do and I understand.
-Anonymous</p>
															</div>
